        "kicker": "HEY BRIDE!",
        "title": "I'm Debbie Flohr",
        "subtitle": "Owner & Artist of Floral Preservation",
        "body": "<p>Flohral Preservation is more than a company; it’s my passion and calling. Destiny brought me into this beautiful, creative field. </p><p>My last name - “Flohr” means “an array of flowers.” So I guess you could say that I was born for this business! After 20 years in the industry, I’ve pioneered new products and techniques that exemplify Flohral Preservation’s core purpose - to leave you with a lifelong work of art that honors those special moments in your life.</p><p></p><p>When I’m not preserving bouquets, I’m usually traveling and chasing the next beautiful flower-filled café or garden. No matter where I go, I’m always drawn to blooms. I’ll always choose to stop and smell the roses, even in the rain, and I bring that same love and inspiration into every piece I create. </p><p></p><p>Above all, I’m a proud single mom to four amazing boys, who have helped me BLOOM into the woman I am today. I’m truly BLESSED & OBSESSED with what I do!</p>",
        "signature_text": "by Debbie Flohr",
